parameters:
There are plenty of [Magic Sewing Tools] available. Let's
make use of them.
Would you like to repair your clothes?
You can hear the sound of a child crying nearby...

\n<Roselitte>"...What are you doing in such a place? Are you a resident
of Annabern?"

\n<Roselitte>"Did you come all the way here by yourself? Or are you lost?
Aren't your parents or any adults with you?"
\n<Roselitte>"Hey, you can't just keep crying like that..."

\n<Ameria>"--There, there. It was scary, wasn't it? It's all right
now. Onee-san will help you out."
Ameria spoke soothingly to the crying child.
\n<Child's voice>"Wow, amazing! It doesn't hurt at all! Thank you, Onee-san!"

\n<Ameria>"I'm glad, I'm glad. It's scary to fall down in a place like
this, isn't it? But you did well to manage on your own!
Hallelujah!♪"

\n<Ameria>"--Roselitte-san, I don't know the details, but it seems
like she escaped here all by herself when the attack
happened. Let's take her back to Annabern."

\n<Roselitte>"Yes. Let's head back and leave her with the soldiers... To
think she escaped all the way here by herself and only ended
up with a sprain. The vitality of children is beyond
expectation."

Roselitte and the others once returned to Annabern and
entrusted the lost child to the soldiers.
